{"tid":388462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人眼中嘅中港融合","createTime":"2017-09-05T13:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T01:15:05.000Z","uid":73231,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2645044d4e2f4ce87654fa022d6170fe90520e","tid":388462,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://toyokeizai.net/articles/-/185975?display=b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoyokeizai.net%2Farticles%2F-%2F185975%3Fdisplay%3Db&d=gJGV%2FGGIthcadGnvJRRIYzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fbdcb656\" target=\"_blank\">http://toyokeizai.net/articles/-/185975?display=b</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸冇香港化<br />\n但香港明顯大陸化<br />\n<br />\n越境雙非幼稚園學生問題<br />\n香港嘅英語同廣東話母語教學同大陸嘅蝗語分別<br />\n<br />\n雙非嘅香港身份問題<br />\n<br />\n以外國人眼中睇完報導又係另一番不是滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21ab7128447be8d98e245a72f0b743e779d05a1","tid":388462,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f77d6a4090f10fa3f1de1a5c6e353a12b59f3f","tid":388462,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"根本除咗舐共嘅人之外全世界都知咩料"},{"pid":"5126f76211de0b0515311b6dd320c53871398d20","tid":388462,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現実は、香港が中国化してしまった。</span>その現実を認めるには、なにも返還記念式典に中国の習近平国家主席がやって来て、「中央政府への挑戦は許さない」と演説して香港の独立気運ににらみを利かせる必要も、閲兵式と称して誰に銃口を向けているかわからない人民解放軍を見せびらかす必要も、実はなかった。<br />\n</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf2c8dc785c5ce8336e8286c26cf1e2793d5841","tid":388462,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"Btw香港人唔係覺得雨革傳唔到出國嘛？<br />\n特別日本又近"}]}